data.name: ReadCaseRoleCsePersonCase
data.value: select T1.CAS_NUMBER, T1.CSP_NUMBER, T1.TYPE, T1.CASE_ROLE_ID, T1.START_DATE, T1.END_DATE, T2.TYPE, T2.BIRTH_PLACE_STATE, T2.CREATED_TIMESTAMP, T2.OUT_OF_WEDLOCK, T2.PAT_ESTAB_IND, T2.DATE_PATERN_ESTAB, T2.BC_FATHER_LAST_NM, T2.BC_FATHER_FIRST_NM, T2.BC_SIGNATURE, T2.HOSPITAL_PAT_EST, T3.INTERSTATE_CASE_ID from CKT_CASE T3 with(readuncommitted) join CKT_CSE_PERSON T2 with(readuncommitted) join CKT_CASE_ROLE T1 with(readuncommitted) on (T2.NUMB = T1.CSP_NUMBER) and (T1.TYPE = 'CH') and (T2.NUMB between cast(@suppPersonNumber1 as char(10)) and cast(@suppPersonNumber2 as char(10))) and (T2.NUMB > @numb) on T3.NUMB = T1.CAS_NUMBER order by T1.CSP_NUMBER

data.name: ReadInterstateRequest
data.value: select top(1) IDENTIFIER, CREATED_TIMESTAMP, OTH_ST_CASE_STATUS, KS_CASE_IND, OTH_STATE_CLS_DTE, CAS_I_NUMBER from CKT_INTERSTAT_RQST with(readuncommitted) where (@casINumber = CAS_I_NUMBER) and (CREATED_TIMESTAMP <= @createdTimestamp) and (KS_CASE_IND = 'N') and ( (OTH_ST_CASE_STATUS <> 'C') or ( (OTH_ST_CASE_STATUS = 'C') and (OTH_STATE_CLS_DTE >= @othStateClsDte) ) )

data.name: ReadLegalActionDetailLegalAction
data.value: select distinct T1.LGA_IDENTIFIER, T1.LA_DETAIL_NO, T1.NON_FIN_OBLG_TYPE, T1.DETAIL_TYPE, T2.CLASSIFICATION, T2.STANDARD_NO, T2.ESTABLISHMENT_CD from CKT_LEGAL_ACTION T2 with(readuncommitted) join CKT_LEGAL_ACT_DTL T1 with(readuncommitted) join CKT_LEGAL_ACT_PERS T3 with(readuncommitted) on (T1.LA_DETAIL_NO = T3.LAD_R_NUMBER) and (T1.LGA_IDENTIFIER = T3.LGA_R_IDENTIFIER) and (T3.ACCOUNT_TYPE = 'R') and (T1.NON_FIN_OBLG_TYPE = 'EP') and (T1.DETAIL_TYPE = 'N') join CKT_CASE_ROLE T5 with(readuncommitted) on (T3.CSP_NUMBER = T5.CSP_NUMBER) and (T5.TYPE = 'AP') and (@casNumber = T5.CAS_NUMBER) join CKT_LEGAL_ACT_PERS T6 with(readuncommitted) on (T1.LA_DETAIL_NO = T6.LAD_R_NUMBER) and (T1.LGA_IDENTIFIER = T6.LGA_R_IDENTIFIER) and (T6.ACCOUNT_TYPE = 'S') and (@cspNumber = T6.CSP_NUMBER) on (T2.LEGAL_ACTION_ID = T1.LGA_IDENTIFIER) and (T2.CLASSIFICATION = 'J')

data.name: ReadOcse157Data
data.value: select top(1) max(RUN_NUMBER) from CKT_OCSE157_DATA with(readuncommitted) where (FISCAL_YEAR = @fiscalYear) and (LINE_NUMBER = '08 ')

data.name: ReadOcse157Verification
data.value: select FISCAL_YEAR, RUN_NUMBER, LINE_NUMBER, COLUMN0, CREATED_TIMESTAMP, CASE_NUMBER, SUPP_PERSON_NUMBER, DATE_OF_BIRTH, PLACE_OF_BIRTH, SOCIAL_SECURITY_NB, CHILD_NAME from CKT_OCSE157_VERIFI where (COLUMN0 <> ' ') and (FISCAL_YEAR = @fiscalYear) and (RUN_NUMBER = @runNumber) and (LINE_NUMBER = '08 ') and (SUPP_PERSON_NUMBER > @suppPersonNumber1) and (SUPP_PERSON_NUMBER between cast(@suppPersonNumber2 as char(10)) and cast(@suppPersonNumber3 as char(10))) order by SUPP_PERSON_NUMBER

data.name: ReadPersonProgram
data.value: select top(1) T1.CSP_NUMBER, T1.EFFECTIVE_DATE, T1.DISCONTINUE_DATE, T1.CREATED_TIMESTAMP, T1.PRG_GENERATED_ID from CKT_PROGRAM T2 with(readuncommitted) join CKT_PERSON_PROGRAM T1 with(readuncommitted) on (@cspNumber = T1.CSP_NUMBER) and (T1.EFFECTIVE_DATE <= @effectiveDate) and (T1.DISCONTINUE_DATE >= @effectiveDate) and (T2.PROGRAM_ID = T1.PRG_GENERATED_ID) and ( T2.CODE in ('AFI', 'FCI', 'MAI', 'NAI') )
